issue.title: [BUG] AttributeError in variable_names check
issue.body:
`[" " in name for name in variable_names].any()` leads to `AttributeError: 'list' object has no attribute 'any'` for me.

https://github.com/MilesCranmer/PySR/blob/edb2cd636d2b052fbc13d18a33f768c869e3aa13/pysr/sr.py#L1136

nodes.body: Thanks, that's definitely a bug. Will fix!
